My experience with this has been the filler neck elbow
coming apart (poke your finger into it all the way
around the opening) and the vent tubes from the top of
the tank pulling loose. I really doubt a charcoal can
problem, but it is remotely possible. Also check the
seal on your rear hatch while you're at it! -BaH

